{"tid":1480698,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《Winter on Fire》導演給香港人一封信：把握現在，機不可失","createTime":"2019-08-17T11:59:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T06:18:34.000Z","uid":54642,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0391bb5b305253ea955d0605ab7e725cc70b447a","tid":1480698,"uid":54642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T11:59:36.000Z","msg":"2015 年在 Netflix 播出的紀錄片《Winter on Fire: Ukraine&rsquo;s Fight for Freedom》紀錄了 2013/14 年「烏克蘭革命」的故事軌跡，因為背景與本港「反對逃犯條例修訂示威」極為相似，近日在香港備受關注。紀錄片的導演&nbsp;Evgeny Afineevsky&nbsp;昨天在 Twitter 貼出「給香港人的信」，表示自己衷心支持港人，勉勵大家堅強團結，並希望大家能夠從他的紀錄片得到啟發。<br />\nEvgeny Afineevsky 表示，烏克蘭革命的關鍵是「人民掌握力量並創造改變」，他強調團結是極之重要的，要成功就要令老幼、貧富、不同社會階層／國籍／種族／宗教的人團結起來。<br />\n他認為年輕一代渴求改變和自由，即使面對子彈仍勇敢站出來，未來的希望就握在他們手上。至於推動年輕人政治覺醒的關鍵，在於大家對民主社會言論自由的追求，現時世界各地都有新的民權運動發起，大家應明白世事萬變，並抱著開放的態度去接受。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://photoblog.hk/258971/%e3%80%8awinter-on-fire%e3%80%8b%e5%b0%8e%e6%bc%94%e7%b5%a6%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e4%ba%ba%e4%b8%80%e5%b0%81%e4%bf%a1%ef%bc%9a%e6%8a%8a%e6%8f%a1%e7%8f%be%e5%9c%a8%ef%bc%8c%e6%a9%9f%e4%b8%8d%e5%8f%af/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2F258971%2F%25e3%2580%258awinter-on-fire%25e3%2580%258b%25e5%25b0%258e%25e6%25bc%2594%25e7%25b5%25a6%25e9%25a6%2599%25e6%25b8%25af%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e4%25b8%2580%25e5%25b0%2581%25e4%25bf%25a1%25ef%25bc%259a%25e6%258a%258a%25e6%258f%25a1%25e7%258f%25be%25e5%259c%25a8%25ef%25bc%258c%25e6%25a9%259f%25e4%25b8%258d%25e5%258f%25af%2F&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmhs8Bcr99949gko4GmpRTno%3D&h=0442e3ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://photoblog.hk/258971/%e3%80%8awinter-on-fire%e3%80%8b%e5%b0%8e%e6%bc%94%e7%b5%a6%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e4%ba%ba%e4%b8%80%e5%b0%81%e4%bf%a1%ef%bc%9a%e6%8a%8a%e6%8f%a1%e7%8f%be%e5%9c%a8%ef%bc%8c%e6%a9%9f%e4%b8%8d%e5%8f%af/</a>"},{"pid":"b43e2915bf4921cf3cd5c3c6125c6d49d7edfc1f","tid":1480698,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T12:00:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asse